title: [Mairiseth Telearat, Cliffwalk]
description: A scattering of flora-stitched maedatha blankets grace the soft, green grasses of the lawn, the center-set garden set beneath the shade of a wide-branched olive tree.  The pathway cuts between the faerthiel-latticed buildings ascending further into the market, while vibrant-colored booths flank the entrance to the bridge, the faenor-railed woodwork arcing across the bluish green waters below the cliffside.
